thread.title: BYRON LEE
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by BYRON LEE

author: BYRON LEE
title: BYRON LEE
text: StoreDJ is not only one of the best run DJ stores around, it's one of the best run businesses around hands down. Customer service is great, staff are knowledgeable, patient and helpful. It is efficient and well organised, and it is easy to find what you are looking for online and in the store, as well as easy to make purchases. I am a loyal, long-term customer.
